<FlowConfigModule>
  <page title="Standard or Itemized Deductions" route="standard-or-itemized">
    <section>
      <h1>Standard or Itemized Deductions</h1>
      <p>Standard or itemized deductions reduce the amount of your income subject to tax.</p>
      <p>Your maximum standard deduction amount is: <fg-show path="/standardDeduction" /></p>
      <p>Your maximum itemized deduction amount is: <fg-show path="/itemizedDeduction" /></p>

      <fg-set
        path="/wantsItemizedDeduction">
        <question content-key="flow.standardized-or-itemized.fields./wantsItemizedDeduction.question" />
        <input type="boolean" />
      </fg-set>

      <h1>Itemized Deductions</h1>
      <h2>Qualified mortgage interest</h2>
      <p>Your total deductible State and Qualified mortgage interest is: <fg-show
          path="/qualifiedMortgageInterestTotal" /></p>
      <fg-collection
        path="/qualifiedMortgageInterest">
        <fg-set path="/qualifiedMortgageInterest/*/interest">
          <question content-key="flow.standardized-or-itemized.fields./qualifiedMortgageInterest/*/interest.question" />
          <input type="dollar" />
        </fg-set>
      </fg-collection>

      <h2>Investment interest (limited to your net investment income)</h2>
      <p>Investment interest (limited to your net investment income)</p>
      <p>Your total deductible State and Local Taxes is: <fg-show
          path="/qualifiedInvestmentInterestExpensesTotal" /></p>
      <fg-collection
        path="/qualifiedInvestmentInterestExpenses"
      >
        <fg-set path="/qualifiedInvestmentInterestExpenses/*/expense">
          <question content-key="flow.standardized-or-itemized.fields./qualifiedInvestmentInterestExpenses/*/expense" />
          <input type="dollar" />
        </fg-set>
      </fg-collection>

      <h2>State and Local Taxes</h2>
      <p>There are four types of State and Local Taxes: 1) State, local, and foreign income taxes;
        2) State and local general sales taxes; 3) State and local real estate taxes; 4) State and
        local personal property taxes</p>
      <p>There is a $40,000 deduction cap on SALT payments</p>
      <p>Your total deductible State and Local Taxes is: <fg-show
          path="/stateAndLocalTaxPaymentsTotal" /></p>
      <fg-collection
        path="/stateAndLocalTaxPayments">
        <fg-set path="/stateAndLocalTaxPayments/*/taxPayment">
          <question content-key="flow.standardized-or-itemized.fields./stateAndLocalTaxPayments/*/taxPayment.question" />
          <input type="dollar" />
        </fg-set>
      </fg-collection>

      <h2>Estimated medical and dental expenses</h2>
      <p>Total expenses that exceed 7.5% of your Estimated medical and dental expenses Can include
        the total estimated amount paid for health insurance premiums, not including any amount the
        employer pays</p>
      <p>Your total deductible State and Local Taxes is: <fg-show
          path="/medicalAndDentalExpensesTotal" /></p>
      <fg-collection
        path="/medicalAndDentalExpenses">
        <fg-set path="/medicalAndDentalExpenses/*/expense">
          <question content-key="flow.standardized-or-itemized.fields./medicalAndDentalExpenses/*/expense.question" />
          <input type="dollar" />
        </fg-set>
      </fg-collection>

      <h2>Charitable Contributions to Qualified Organizations</h2>
      <p>Your total deductible Charitable Contributions to Qualified Organizations is: <fg-show
          path="/charitableContributionsTotal" /></p>
      <fg-collection
        path="/charitableContributions">
        <fg-set path="/charitableContributions/*/contribution">
          <question content-key="flow.standardized-or-itemized.fields./charitableContributions/*/contribution.question" />
          <input type="dollar" />
        </fg-set>
      </fg-collection>

      <h2>Casualty Losses</h2>
      <p>Your total deductible Casualty Losses is: <fg-show path="/casualtyLossesTotal" /></p>
      <p>Casualty and theft losses relating to your home, household items, and vehicles if
        the loss took place in a federally declared disaster area</p>
      <fg-collection
        path="/casualtyLosses">
        <fg-set path="/casualtyLosses/*/loss">
          <question content-key="flow.standardized-or-itemized.fields./casualtyLosses/*/loss.question" />
          <input type="dollar" />
        </fg-set>
      </fg-collection>

      <h2>Other Deductions</h2>
      <p>Your total deductible Other Deductions is: <fg-show path="/otherDeductionsTotal" /></p>
      <fg-collection
        path="/otherDeductions">
        <fg-set path="/otherDeductions/*/payment">
          <question content-key="flow.standardized-or-itemized.fields./otherDeductions/*/payment.question" />
          <input type="dollar" />
        </fg-set>
      </fg-collection>

    </section>
  </page>
</FlowConfigModule>
